    "7104525": {
        "Desc": "Strike the large purified crystal",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "Great, you're back!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yup, we're back!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "There've been several earthquakes ever since you went through that gate. We don't know what's going on down there, but we're glad to see that you're both okay."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, you don't look too bad yourself. Looks like the rest helped, eh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "How are things on your end?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "I've followed your advice and rested here all this while. I'm feeling a whole lot better now... Was this all due to \"that thing\" behind the gate?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "I didn't go in there, but I could feel some strange pulsing within... Something amazing must have been back there, I'm sure of it..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "*cough* I grew up listening to tales of the Yakshas, and some of my seniors used to say that one of them was sealed inside The Chasm and slumbers to this day."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Well, we didn't meet this Yaksha you speak of..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "I see... Thank you. So, as for the dark mud we... *cough* Sorry..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "There was a huge floating crystal in there..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "So that's the key to solving the mystery of The Chasm... I might go and see it for myself later."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "*cough* Thank you. So, as for that dark mud... *cough* Sorry..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It hasn't been completely cleared out yet."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It'll experience a gradual retreat."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yup, now that we've removed the taint from that large crystal, that stinky mud should be back underground in no time!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "I understand... *cough* I'll inform the other team members. It seems that our exploration of The Chasm... has met with some initial success."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "This is way stronger than that time at Qiaoying Village..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Any future plans?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Are you all leaving?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "\"Qiaoying Village\"? What's that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "Hmm? It's the most famous teahouse in Liyue. Top notch scenery, top-notch tea... You haven't heard of it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "Well, not that I like the place very much... Even if it is my second home after Mingyun Village. I know every last creek and tree in that place like the back of my hand."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "I guess I would've remembered the place and the people more fondly if it wasn't for that disagreement I had with that one commission-giver while on a map-making assignment... Eh, whatever. No point talking about that now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "And well, I say I don't like the place, but if I do achieve something great this time, it would be good to go back there to rest... The old man's tea is a truly unforgettable experience, after all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "But over to more pleasant thoughts... The next time I'm back home, I'll be a famous adventurer having tea with the old man, you know? I do hope you'll be there to see it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "...Heh, there I go again, talking about unrealistic stuff."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "Well, we could use this opportunity to become an official exploratory team under the Ministry of Civil Affairs... But I don't think we'll be going anywhere any time soon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "After all, it was due to your spelunking that we were able to avoid the perils of the path, such that no one was injured or lost, and that our material losses proved negligible."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "I think that we might stay here for a while yet, help the Ministry staff watch over the underground anomalies, and maintain the exploration facilities."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Did you encounter any strangers after we left?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "What? Hmm... Well, I didn't see anyone on the way back and I fell asleep pretty quickly once I got back to camp, so I didn't see anyone else pass by."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "What's wrong? What's with the sudden question?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm, never mind, it's nothing..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "*cough* Well, if you're leaving, don't forget to say hi to Muning as well... *cough* Tell him... that I'm gonna be promoted. Who knows who's gonna be the boss of who before long, eh?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7104515": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Clitopho",
                    "T": "Ah, you're here! Welcome to the Chasm Exploration Team's demolitions team base and water point!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Clitopho",
                    "T": "We — by which I mean I, Clitopho — salute you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Clitopho",
                    "T": "Come, come, have a drink! Consider it my treat — just a little something for all you've done for me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What's next for you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Will you be sticking around?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Clitopho",
                    "T": "Well, I'm an official member of the team now, so since they're staying, I'm staying."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Clitopho",
                    "T": "Well, things would certainly be easier if Khedive and Jinwu could get me some extra help..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Clitopho",
                    "T": "Though that said, I wouldn't be able to call myself the sole member *and* team leader if that were to happen."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
