    "7104415": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "Don't worry, I won't run off. Just retrieve the Lumenstone Adjuvant, and things should go fine."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7104416": {
        "Desc": "Use the cage-shaped object to destroy the three remaining Bedrock Keys",
        "Tips": "Open the Inventory to view the map that Zhiqiong drew for you",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "Honestly, I'm not too sure about how the Bedrock Key works, but you could start from looking into those cage-shaped Geo elemental formations over there."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What is that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "These strange formations have been puzzling the Ministry of Civil Affairs for some time now. They seem to have grown up from the bedrock of The Chasm over the last two years, and their properties are very similar to those of the \"thing\" underground."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "We say this because they can undergo some kind of disintegration when under the influence of the anomalies."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "Later, Huishan Hall's investigations revealed that they have been absorbing Geo elemental energy from the surroundings, slowly eroding the structure of the Bedrock Keys..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "It is a most ominous phenomenon, almost like something is consciously trying to break the sealing array."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "We have to clear them out twice every month, but they will always grow back quickly... and they have only grown back quicker over time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "Perhaps that \"thing\" below is growing restless... and that is why the Qixing has sent us to investigate."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7104417": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "Please don't talk to me for the time being, or I'll get in trouble again..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "\"Again\"...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "Uh, just don't sweat that..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7104418": {
        "Desc": "Use the cage-shaped object to destroy the three remaining Bedrock Keys",
        "Tips": "Open the Inventory to view the map that Zhiqiong drew for you",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "Very impressive! That should be the last one. With this, the array sealing The Chasm has dissipated, and we can explore the area underground."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "That said... We should probably go and pay Muning a visit first. Hmph, not that he's going to do anything other than scold us, though."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7104419": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Muning",
                    "T": "See? What did I say? You weren't guarding the warehouse as you should've at all!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Muning",
                    "T": "You've really done it this time, Zhiqiong. How are we going to resolve this matter, huh? Are you going to take responsibility for undoing the array of your own accord? Can you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Muning",
                    "T": "Ah, you're here. *sigh* So... how are you going to explain destroying the Bedrock Keys?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "From an aesthetic point of view, this place looks better without them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Muning",
                    "T": "You...! Ugh, alright! You're taking responsibility for this. As for the rest, we'll wait for the Qixing to make their judgment first."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "Hehe, don't you worry, Muning only gets mad at people who don't care. Otherwise, he's just a worrywart — not a bad person."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "Well, let's leave his stubborn temper aside first. Once you're ready, I'll round everyone up to follow you down into the mines."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "If you really wanted to stop me, you'd have chased me off some time ago now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "Our purpose this time is to reach the deepest level of The Chasm, map it, and... uh, investigate the source of the anomalies."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "Ah, yes, I almost forgot — welcome to the Chasm Exploration Team!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "If you'll allow me a bit of your time, let me introduce you to the team."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "This is Khedive, a scholar specifically called in from Sumeru. His specialties are ores and biology. He's this exploration team's leading man... well, in scientific and financial matters, at least."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "This is Jinwu, who's in charge of safety. The repair and maintenance of any facilities we use and our security is ensured by her."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "And this is... Taliesin. He's a bard from Mondstadt... and goodness knows why he insisted on coming down here with us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "Also, perhaps you'll discover new allies once you get down into the mines, eh? Haha, who knows?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "And last but not least, you have me, the super hands-on surveyor! My job is to help scout the way forward and draw maps, which I'll share with you all, of course!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "Well, please head over to the crane by the mines once you're ready. Originally, it was meant to transport goods, but it can also bring a few people up and down the mines, no problem!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiqiong",
                    "T": "Hmm, that said, since you have your wind glider, I suppose that you'd be fine even without the crane, eh?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
