    "7104420": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Muning",
                    "T": "If you understood what I said at all, please stop hanging around this place."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Muning",
                    "T": "If not..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "If not...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Muning",
                    "T": "*sigh* If not nothing, really. All I can do is write weekly reports."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Weekly reports?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Muning",
                    "T": "Just a somewhat bothersome, meaningless, but nonetheless necessary document."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Why don't you just stop writing them?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Muning",
                    "T": "That won't do. I have to at least inform people that you've shown up here, you know?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Muning",
                    "T": "The last report was sent out yesterday. In other words, the Ministry of Civil Affairs should get word of your presence here in a couple of days."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Muning",
                    "T": "When that happens, someone might actually drop by and forcibly get you to leave."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Muning",
                    "T": "So you're free to act before then, got it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Got it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Muning",
                    "T": "That's good. Hmph, if it wasn't for your great deeds in Liyue's service... Eh, you know what? Forget it."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
